************************************TwitterFriends*******************************************

TwitterFriends it's a JQuery Plugins that show an autocomplete component every time that you insert a @ simbol in 
the textfield that it's attached to the plugin.

To use TwitterFriends just import the js and css fields of the plugin and initialize the component whith the next
code

TwitterFriends.Init(TWITTER_USER_ID_OR_USER_NAME, INPUT_FIELD);

The first parameter is the Twitter user_id or the user_name(whitout @) of the user that you whant to get it's fiends,
The second parmeter is the input field where you whant to show the autocomplete.

TwitterFriends only work with JQuery >= 1.7